      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：咸其腓，凶，居吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows one moving the calves of his leg. There will be evil. If he abide (quiet in his place), there will be good fortune.</seg>
